{"tid":1428682,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"認真，下次再見到便衣想的人走，可否夾手夾腳救番出黎","createTime":"2019-08-07T10:38:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T11:06:07.000Z","uid":252960,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"8e09953e17e56b6cba728c3cd9f7eafc7a3ecefb","tid":1428682,"uid":252960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:38:01.000Z","msg":"步驟：<br />\n1. 手足被便衣逗，大聲嗌，吸引街坊圍觀<br />\n2. 要趁佢哋未call馬前令件事發酵，上到連登或TG<br />\n3. 住喺附近，及有面罩既巴打見到post，即刻上裝，衝去現場<br />\n4. 喺街坊包圍之下，將手足從狗爪拉出<br />\n5. 街坊形成人鏈唔比狗去捉人<br />\n我知唔易，但啲便衣狗最薄裝，已經係救人最佳時機，你等佢call到重裝狗過黎，已經太遲"},{"pid":"56ff0f6fd004cba0bcd44be79c0f81f363a6bb8c","tid":1428682,"uid":69472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:38:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a1dd14b7bf600f0b87ff2ee8fb0f81233d7329a6","tid":1428682,"uid":167938,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:40:55.000Z","msg":"打鳩佢啦 屌"},{"pid":"ddfe520ba6fbe1543dcc82961d7fd2bab99ca67e","tid":1428682,"uid":252960,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a1dd14b7bf600f0b87ff2ee8fb0f81233d7329a6","tid":1428682,"uid":167938,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:40:55.000Z","msg":"打鳩佢啦 屌"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:43:47.000Z","msg":"打又唔好，盞比位對家入，我相信只要有一個巴打肯做拉人嗰個，街坊就會配合"},{"pid":"344dcdf79593e51404ddb7d16f7c502dd27d4285","tid":1428682,"uid":252960,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:44:24.000Z","msg":"佢夠疆就告哂所有街坊阻差辦公"},{"pid":"785ecbdecdae3294b218e1c360feadcb2027bd14","tid":1428682,"uid":126309,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ddfe520ba6fbe1543dcc82961d7fd2bab99ca67e","tid":1428682,"uid":252960,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a1dd14b7bf600f0b87ff2ee8fb0f81233d7329a6","tid":1428682,"uid":167938,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:40:55.000Z","msg":"打鳩佢啦 屌"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:43:47.000Z","msg":"打又唔好，盞比位對家入，我相信只要有一個巴打肯做拉人嗰個，街坊就會